    <text>
        <body>
            
            <div1 type="letter">
                
                <pb facs="nei.j4a.26c.8a"/>
                
                <fw type="curatorial">8</fw>
                
                <opener>
                    <dateline>
                        Wellsville, Mo.
                        Oct. 8 - 58
                    </dateline>
                    
                    <salute>Dear Sirs:</salute>
                </opener>
                <p>I am 78. I know Montana and the Dakotas.</p>
                
                <p>I sit enthralled as I listen to Dr. Neihard<sic>Neihardt</sic> read his beautifully descriptive worded <hi rend="underline">Epic</hi> of <hi rend="underline">America</hi>. He reads with such deep feeling.</p>
                <closer>
                    <salute>Sincerely</salute>
                
                    <signed>(Mrs) Linnie Noel</signed>
                </closer>
                
                <note type="recipeint">
                    ansd 
                    10-30-58
                </note>
                
                <ab type="postmark">
                    WELLSVILLE
                    OCT 2
                    5 - PM
                    1958
                    MO.
                </ab>
                <figure>
                    <figDesc>1 Cent Stamp</figDesc>
                    <p><unclear>WASHINGTON</unclear>
                    1Â¢
                    U.S. POSTAGE</p>
                </figure>
                <figure>
                    <figDesc>2 Cent Stamp</figDesc>
                    <p>UNITED STATES
                    2 CENTS
                    FRANKLIN
                    POSTAL CARD</p>
                </figure>
                
                THIS SIDE OF CARD IS FOR ADDRESS
                
                <ab type="address">
                    <address>
                        <addrLine>Epic of America</addrLine>
                            <addrLine>Mo. University</addrLine>
                                <addrLine>Columbia</addrLine>
